    "The minimum MAE achieved by the proposed approach is 0.788661 and obtained when K is 60, thus this value is selected as the optimal value of the K parameter for the given dataset.",
    "Further, the minimum achieved MAE values for the standard item-based CF and semantically enhanced CF competing approaches are 0.866752 and 0.803506, respectively.",
    "However, the proposed approach result indicates effective improvement in prediction accuracy for all K parameter values when compared with other competing approaches.",
    "Improvement Extent for Sparsity ProblemIn this experiment, the effectiveness of the proposed approach in handling the sparsity problem is investigated and examined against other considered benchmark approaches.",
    "Sparsity is one of the main problems that negatively influence the prediction accuracy of CF recommendation approaches."
